        function InitializeRequest(sender, args) 
        {
            if (prm.get_isInAsyncPostBack() & args.get_postBackElement().id == 'bt_abort')
            {
                args.set_cancel(true);
            }
        }
        function EndRequestHandler(sender, args)
        {
          if (args.get_error() != undefined)
          {
            if (args.get_error().name == "Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManagerParserErrorException")
            {
                var errorMessage = args.get_error().message;
                if (errorMessage.indexOf("Sessi") != -1)
                {
                    alert("Session timeout.");
                    args.set_errorHandled(true);
                }
            }
          }
        }
        function AbortPostBack() 
        {
            if (prm.get_isInAsyncPostBack()) 
            {
                prm.abortPostBack();
            }
        } 
        
        function TreeViewOnClick()
        {
            var txt = event.srcElement.getAttribute("site_map_id");
            var urltxt = event.srcElement.getAttribute("url");
            var urlele = document.getElementById("ctl00_hdTreeURL");
            var ele = document.getElementById("ctl00_hdTreeSelected");
            var btn = document.getElementById("ctl00_btnTreeSelected");
            if (urltxt != "" && urltxt != null) {
                ele.value = txt;
                urlele.value = urltxt;
                event.srcElement.parentElement.setAttribute('href','#');
                btn.click();
            }
        }
        
       
        function ServerRedirectPage(url)
        {
            var ele = document.getElementById("ctl00_hdTreeSelected");
            var urlele = document.getElementById("ctl00_hdTreeURL");
            var btn = document.getElementById("ctl00_btnTreeSelected");
            ele.value = "";
            urlele.value = url;
            btn.click();
        }

            var tbDate=document.getElementById('ctl00_cphPage_tx_Date');
 
            for(i=0;i<rbLength;i++)
            {

		            switch (action)
		            {

			                if (tbDate.value=="") tbDate.value='01/01/0001';
				            if (CheckingDate(tbDate.value))
				            {
					            window.open('F173_SelectSD.aspx?CustSeqNo='+strCustNo+'&WorkList='+tbPreferredWorkList.value+'&Date='+tbDate.value);

				            }
				            break;

				            break; 
				            case 3:

					            //window.open('F001_CreatePR.aspx?CustSeqNo='+strCustNo+'&TemplateType='+tbPreferredWorkList.value+'&SDClass=CUST');

					            document.getElementById('ctl00_cphPage_btn_CustServDetail').click();

				           break;				           
				           case 6:

    <script type="text/javascript">
// expand and highlight
function MasterExpandTree(valuepath)
{
    if (valuepath == "")
        return;
    var paths = valuepath.split("/");
    for (var i=0;i<paths.length-1;i++)
    {
        var divele = document.getElementById(paths[i]);
        if (divele != null)
        {
            var command = divele.parentElement.getAttribute("href");
            eval(command);
        }
    }
    
}
 
var winid = document.getElementById("ctl00_hdWindowID");
if (window.name != "") {
    winid.value = window.name;
}
else {
    window.name = "Wparent";
    winid.value = "Wparent";
}
 
// expand and highlight
var collapseAll = "N";
if (collapseAll != "Y") {
    var sitemapele = document.getElementById("ctl00_hdSiteMapList");
    var sitemaplist = eval(sitemapele.value);
    if (sitemaplist != null) {
        for (var i=0;i<sitemaplist.length;i++)
        {
            var sitemapnode = sitemaplist[i];
            if (sitemapnode.WindowName == window.name)
            {
                if (sitemapnode.SiteMapID != "") {
                    var cele = document.getElementById(sitemapnode.SiteMapID);
                    if (cele != null) {
                        cele.style.backgroundColor = 'Gainsboro';
                        var vpath = cele.getAttribute("path");
                        MasterExpandTree(vpath);
                    }
                }
            }        
        }
    }
}
 
    </script>
